-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">GIC</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">、</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Index Ventures</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">、</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Khosla Ventures</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">、</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Lightspeed</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">、</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">T. Rowe Price&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">及&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">WCM Investment Management&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">参与跟投。</span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">自</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">5&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">月份&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Khosla Ventures&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">等投资机构给出&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">63.5&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">亿美元估值以来，</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">ClickHouse&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">的估值已增加数十亿美元。联合创始人兼首席执行官&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Aaron Katz&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: lef