ing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Polymarket&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">达成新合作或拓展了现有合作。</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">ClickHouse&nbsp;</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">总部位于硅谷，在荷兰及其他国家设有办事处。</span></span></font></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:16px;outline:0px;visibility:visible;white-space:normal;letter-spacing:1.5px;font-size:15px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:2;text-align:justify;margin-right:16px;\"><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">\"</span></span></font><font face=\"宋体\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">我们公司的一个独特之处在于，超过半数的客户、过半营收以及半数以上员工都分布在北美以外地区，</span></span></font><font face=\"Calibri\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"outline: 0px;visibility: visible;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 0.544px;text-align: left;\"><span textstyle=\"